snippet.title: Johnny Depp Speaks on Why Amber Heard has Not Been Fired Yet!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Speaks on Why Amber Heard has Not Been Fired Yet!
Amber Heard has filed a lawsuit against her ex-husband Johnny Depp, claiming that he abused her verbally and physically. Depp filed a defamation case against Heard after evidence of his innocence appeared in the form of a leaked tape from 2015 and a statement from her hairdresser. However, in an unforeseen turn of events, Heard might face not just millions of dollars in penalties, but also three years in jail.
